{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a101a9548","title":"致老师的大字报","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（三）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年10月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"191ed4843e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"7a101a9548"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"c181cad286","name":"天镇中学学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"91e7de2364","type":"title","text":"致老师的大字报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"a7a3647e31","type":"authors","text":"山西天镇中学学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"ab2341e1b3","type":"appellation","text":"亲爱的老师们：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"23ce9f924d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们也知道你们是受了很大的委屈，但是你们都是经过革命锻炼，都经得起考验。我们相信你们一定很同情我们的正义行动，当看到你们忧愁的脸，我们心也痛，可是希望老师们不要作了拍马屁的人。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"0421f7ab40","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"ce7594c76c","type":"appellation","text":"撕传单的老师们注意","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"42d9d41037","type":"paragraph","text":"你们如果想解决中学的问题，必须达到我们的要求，此外，因你们撕传单的行为不对，应该在全体同学面前认错，不然，我们坚决斗争！我们决不罢休！！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"3a94b6f72d","type":"paragraph","text":"决不停止运动！！！一定坚持到胜利！！！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"e1b87036a9","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"f2c775eed2","type":"subtitle","text":"“暴露狰狞面目”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"f38b920a75","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）今天是","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"ea4724e77e","type":"paragraph","text":"郭老师是好意，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"99bf6b0846","type":"paragraph","text":"撕下标语保存起，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"72408283d9","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们误会你，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"38905f86e6","type":"paragraph","text":"可把你幸幸的。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"a7b05b6513","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）今天是","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"561fe5d282","type":"paragraph","text":"早晨你到五班去，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"a44b08801a","type":"paragraph","text":"得意洋洋领功里，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"1d1e72d416","type":"paragraph","text":"你的话怎说的，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"994a12b3d0","type":"paragraph","text":"卑鄙无耻臭言论。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"866bea0385","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）你是我们的钱财迷，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"d3f26b30cf","type":"paragraph","text":"因而不来说真理，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"488349bea3","type":"paragraph","text":"你的面目已暴露，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"d3f8370b30","type":"paragraph","text":"还想把我们麻到底。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"db16546873","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）然而你有这行动，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"76d054f04b","type":"paragraph","text":"呼吁标语撕下来，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"db0f483b70","type":"paragraph","text":"撕的快来而写的繁，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"e20c09a19a","type":"paragraph","text":"群众力量打倒你。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"fb7f0bd49c","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"0cbb6e6756","type":"appellation","text":"全体老师们、同学们：","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"3769277d10","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能奴颜，不能媚骨，我们起来吧！我们都知道，今早有出现的，勇敢的，坚毅的，值得我们同学敬佩的贴出了一批“密件”，结果被校方无理地、卑鄙地撕去，请问你们是啥行为？你们讲言论自由，难道是口是心非吗？你们经常批评旧社会压制言论，这不是一丘之貉吗？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"11d3041922","type":"paragraph","text":"尤其是郭丕基老师，你的历史知识那里去了。难道你是继承镇压“一二九”爱国运动的刽子手吗？否则，你为什么压制言论自由。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"d594dd9871","type":"paragraph","text":"老师们，把你们真正的心灵放在人间吧！你们不要无动于衷；不要抑人鼻息，不应被几个臭钱冲昏头脑。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"98a605bf8f","type":"paragraph","text":"起来吧！声援我们吧！","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"},{"id":"8f8803ff3c","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548"}],"page":{"id":"3ce0fb98ed","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a101a9548","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}